Eviden Game System
[Software System]

Allows Players to play the
game. Rounds to be  played and advice to be
generated

Eviden Management System
[Software System]

Allows Managers to create and manage games. Allows Managers to view results of all playeers.

Web Application
[Container: Java Springboot]

Delivers the static content and the game page applications

Single Page Game Application
[Container: Java Springboot 
& React]

Provides all the game functionality to the users via their web browser

API Application
[Container: Java Springboot]

Provides Game Functionality via Json Websockets

Single Page Management Application
[Container: Java Springboot 
& React]

Provides all Management functionality to Game Masters via their web browser

Game System
[Software System]

Stores all information about the game, rounds and advice

Databases
[container: JPA Repositories]

Stores game information like cards, round, games, players

Single Page Game Application
[Container: Java Springboot 
& React]

Provides all the game functionality to the users via their web browser

Single Page Management Application
[Container: Java Springboot 
& React]

Provides all Management functionality to Game Masters via their web browser

Card Service
[Container: Java Springboot]

Provides all the Card functionality to the app via Kafka Messaging

Game Service
[Container: Java Springboot]

Provides all the Game functionality to the app via Kafka Messaging

Lobby Service
[Container: Java Springboot]

Provides all the Lobby functionality to the app via Kafka Messaging

Round Service
[Container: Java Springboot]

Provides all the Round functionality to the app via Kafka Messaging

Game App BFF
[Container: Java Springboot]

Provides all the game functionality to the users via their web browser

Lobby Databases
[container: JPA Repositories]

Stores Lobby Information like players, round and size

Card Databases
[container: JPA Repositories]

Stores Card Information like types, sets and translations

Game Databases
[container: JPA Repositories]

Stores Game Information like rounds, players and resluts

Round Databases
[container: JPA Repositories]

Stores Round information like Players, Cards and Results
